258
0:14:59.08,000 --> 0:15:03,000
One single school striker will always be one single school striker --

259
0:15:03.363,000 --> 0:15:04,000
well, Greta Thunberg.

260
0:15:04.822,000 --> 0:15:07,000
Two, five, ten, one thousand people striking school are a movement,

261
0:15:08.041,000 --> 0:15:09,000
