0:15:45.364,000 --> 0:15:5,000
have no intention of changing the game they're profiting from most,

273
0:15:50.391,000 --> 0:15:52,000
so there's no point in further relying on them.

274
0:15:54.308,000 --> 0:15:55,000
That's scary, I know.

275
0:15:56.341,000 --> 0:16:,000
That's a huge responsibility, a huge burden on everyone's shoulders, yes.

276
0:16:01.716,000 --> 0:16:02,000
But this also means,

277
0:16:03.608,000 --> 0:16:04,000
if we want to,

278
0:16:05.857,000 --> 0:16:06,000
